data.title: AMBIG in Arizona
data.description:
The AMBIG team took a filming trip through Arizona in January of 2012. The best of which was held onto for our feature length presentation.

Featuring AMBIG riders Matt Bennett, Sid Melvin, Sean Conover, Clive Dixon(flow) and Gonzo Hernandez(flow) with a guest appearance by Billy Marks.

Shot By:
Brian Hanson: RED Scarlet X, Canon Lenses
Adam Mills: Panasonic HVX200
Brian Young: Canon 7d

Music:
Cat Party, "Broken English"

Geographic guidance:
Joe Hammeke

Edit:
Brian Hanson

data.title: AMBIG in N.Y.C. & Boston
data.description:
AMBIG riders Corey Duffel, Jt Aultz(not shown), Matt Bennett and Clint Walker spent ten days skating in Boston and New York last August. We only had three demos which allowed us to focus on shooting photos and collecting clips for our upcoming video.

Shot with Panasonic hvx200, Canon 7d

Videography: Brian Hanson, Brian Young

Talent Management: Brian Young

Photo Support: Dan Zaslavsky

Geographical Guidance: Bryan Wright, Allan Ying

Edit: Brian Hanson

Song: Chapterhouse, "Treasure"
